import nltk
for fileid in wordlists.fileids():
    news_text = wordlists.words(fileid)
    fdist = nltk.FreqDist(w.lower() for w in news_text)
    modals = ['can','could','would','might','will']
    print (fileid)
    for m in modals:
        
        print(m + ':',fdist[m], end = ' ')
    print ('\n')
